oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Sunway Vitamins' Program 3 featuring: Buddy Starcher
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: First recording is a Buddy Starcher radio transcription sponsored by Sunway Vitamins, circa late 1940s. Labeled as program number VI M (possibly for 'master', unconfirmed). Second recording is Buddy Starcher radio transcription sponsored by Sunway Vitamins, circa late 1940s. Labeled as program number VII M (possibly for 'master', unconfirmed).
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Buddy Starcher
